From 4368f9510537f4013c24489c53454c8b57d1b28f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GitHub Copilot <copilot@github.com>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 09:20:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] docs: fix documentation inconsistencies

- Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md: fix pnpm installation command from
  'npm install -g @pnpm' to 'npm install -g pnpm' (no @ prefix)

- Quickstart-on-how-to-write-tests.md: update test examples from
  Mocha/Chai patterns to Vitest patterns:
  - Replace 'import { assert } from "chai"' with vitest imports
  - Replace 'import { Context } from "mocha"' with VitestTestContext
  - Update beforeEach/afterEach to use arrow functions with (ctx) param
  - Replace 'this.currentTest' with ctx in Recorder constructor
  - Replace 'createRecorder(this)' with 'createRecorder(ctx)'

- resolve-pnpm-lock-merge-conflict.md: fix missing '/' separator in
  the combined git add command at end of file

- using-azure-identity.md:
  - Update DefaultAzureCredential chain to list all 7 credential types
    (was only listing 2: EnvironmentCredential + ManagedIdentityCredential)
  - Update InteractiveBrowserCredential from outdated 'implicit grant flow'
    to current 'Authorization Code Flow with PKCE'
  - Remove stale NOTE claiming InteractiveBrowserCredential only works in
    browser (it supports Node.js as well)

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
